{
  "stem": "19550.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, you know, the school and the synagogues and even the slaughter house, everything was filled with people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it-- it backed into the officers and the guard room of the gendarmerie, and one of the plans that we were hatching and trying to figure out how we could do it was to break into that guard house and you know, do away with whatever gendarmes you could and-- and get their weapons.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, it never came to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We never-- and this is another element and aspect if it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It holds true in-- in many ways, for other areas, of course, and for the whole question of-- of resistance.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the whole question of time, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before you could, and perhaps there was something conscience-- conscious about this, and planful on the part of-- of the Germans, there was really never any time to-- to organize or to plan or-- or to carry out any kind of plan.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before you knew it, the circumstances changed so drastically that, no matter what your plans were, you couldn't-- you couldn't carry them out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were already taken away or-- or-- or killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This is, by the way, one of the very important [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] philosophical, cum practical questions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole concept of time in the Holocaust was something that was beyond the normal human circumstances.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No one really can, who has not been there, can appreciate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this is just one really relatively smaller element of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the-- the circumstances were so unpredictable, so unreliable, so swiftly changing that certainly in-- in our ghetto, but-- but every place else in the camps and-- and in the other ghettos, that you could not plan and you could not for sure plan.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
